{
  "stem": "20021.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the story of the Haggadah, you know, with-- with the slavery in Egypt and being redeemed from that slavery and Joseph sending-- selling his brothers to, you know-- to these merchants who came by, and then Joseph ending up in Egypt and advising Pharoah, this is fascinating story.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's probably the greatest literature I've ever read, after I've since then read so many books.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that is really fascinating.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And maybe that's why Passover meant so much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, you ate only matzoh, which was a little different than other foods.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and the house had to be cleaned, swept from everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And dishes had to be different dishes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My mother had two sets of dishes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So for Passover all dishes were swept clean and hidden away, and new dishes would come up and all this, so--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my mother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she had help.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had-- she had a matter of fact two maids.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One was a Jewish maid, whom she trusted with the cooking and all that, because she knew how to prepare kosher.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one was a Gentile maid that did the work mostly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Full-time.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember Hanukkah because Hanukkah was a holiday where we played a lot of games.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we're not supposed to play cards all year long, except on Hanukkah you got permission to play cards.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But of course, the-- the game with dreidel was the most peculiar and special for Hannukah, where this is a top that you spin with your fingers.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And depending on the letter that falls down, you win money or lose money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So game-- Hannukah was great in that sense, that we played games with a large crowd.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Families, friends would come and we all would play dreidel together.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
